TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT SHIPMENT_CANCEL_SUMMARY.ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, SHIPMENT_CANCEL_SUMMARY.DC_CODE as DC_CODE, SHIPMENT_CANCEL_SUMMARY.CURRENT_MONTH_SHIPMENTS as CURRENT_MONTH_SHIPMENTS, SHIPMENT_CANCEL_SUMMARY.CURRENT_MONTH_CANCELS as CURRENT_MONTH_CANCELS, SHIPMENT_CANCEL_SUMMARY.PREVIOUS_WEEK_SHIPMENTS as PREVIOUS_WEEK_SHIPMENTS, SHIPMENT_CANCEL_SUMMARY.PREVIOUS_WEEK_CANCELS as PREVIOUS_WEEK_CANCELS, SHIPMENT_CANCEL_SUMMARY.PREVIOUS_MONTH_SHIPMENTS as PREVIOUS_MONTH_SHIPMENTS, SHIPMENT_CANCEL_SUMMARY.PREVIOUS_MONTH_CANCELS as PREVIOUS_MONTH_CANCELS, SHIPMENT_CANCEL_SUMMARY.THREE_MONTHS_SHIPMENTS as THREE_MONTHS_SHIPMENTS, SHIPMENT_CANCEL_SUMMARY.LAST_YEAR_CURR_MTH_SHIPMENTS as LAST_YEAR_CURR_MTH_SHIPMENTS FROM SHIPMENT_CANCEL_SUMMARY SHIPMENT_CANCEL_SUMMARY WHERE SHIPMENT_CANCEL_SUMMARY.AS_OF_DATE= (SELECT MAX(AS_OF_DATE) FROM SHIPMENT_CANCEL_SUMMARY)

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT LCA_PRIORITY_SEQ.CLASS_UPDATE AS CLASS_UPDATE, LCA_PRIORITY_SEQ.RANK1 AS RANK1, LCA_PRIORITY_SEQ.STYLE_NUM AS STYLE_NUM, LCA_PRIORITY_SEQ.COLOR_CODE AS COLOR_CODE, LCA_PRIORITY_SEQ.SIZE_CODE AS SIZE_CODE, LCA_PRIORITY_SEQ.ATTRIBUTION_CODE AS ATTRIBUTION_CODE FROM ( -- LOKUP GENERATED QUERY SELECT LPS.CLASS_UPDATE AS CLASS_UPDATE, RANK () OVER ( PARTITION BY STYLE_NUM, COLOR_CODE, SIZE_CODE, ATTRIBUTION_CODE, SKU, CUP_SIZE ORDER BY LPS.PRIORITY ) AS RANK1, I.STYLE_NUM AS STYLE_NUM, I.COLOR_CODE AS COLOR_CODE, I.SIZE_CODE AS SIZE_CODE, I.ATTRIBUTION_CODE AS ATTRIBUTION_CODE
FROM SKU_LIFECYCLE_CLASS SKC JOIN ITEM I ON SKC.ITEM_ID = I.ITEM_ID JOIN LCA_PRIORITY_SEQ LPS ON LPS.LCA_VALUE = SKC.LIFECYCLE_CODE WHERE SKC.START_DATE <= (SELECT MAX(AS_OF_DATE) FROM SLBA.TASER) AND SKC.END_DATE >= (SELECT MAX(AS_OF_DATE) FROM SLBA.TASER) ) LCA_PRIORITY_SEQ ORDER BY STYLE_NUM, COLOR_CODE, SIZE_CODE, ATTRIBUTION_CODE , RANK1 -- --

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: STYLE_NUM = STYLE_CD AND COLOR_CODE = COLOR_CD AND SIZE_CODE = SIZE_CD AND ATTRIBUTION_CODE = ATTRIBUTE_CD

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MAX(a.AWD_UNITS) as AWD_UNITS, sum(case when a.DEMAND_DATE < (SYSDATE + 14) then a.OPEN_EVENT_UNITS else 0 end) as NET_EVENT_QTY_RNG_1 , sum(case when a.DEMAND_DATE between (SYSDATE + 14) and (SYSDATE + 28) then a.OPEN_EVENT_UNITS else 0 end) as NET_EVENT_QTY_RNG_2 , sum(case when a.DEMAND_DATE > (SYSDATE + 28) then a.OPEN_EVENT_UNITS else 0 end) as NET_EVENT_QTY_RNG_3 , a.ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, LTRIM(RTRIM(a.PLANT_CD)) as PLANT_CD FROM DEMAND a GROUP BY a.ITEM_ID,a.PLANT_CD

END),0) OH_ALLOC_TIL, NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE '%TIL%' THEN NVL(IT_ALLOC,0) END),0) IT_ALLOC_TIL, NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE '%TIL%' THEN NVL(PO_ALLOC,0) END),0) PO_ALLOC_TIL, NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE '%TIL%' THEN NVL(FIRM_WIP_ALLOC,0) END),0) FIRM_WIP_ALLOC_TIL, NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE '%Customer%' THEN NVL(OH_ALLOC,0) END),0) OH_ALLOC_CUST, NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE '%Customer%' THEN NVL(IT_ALLOC,0) END),0) IT_ALLOC_CUST, NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE '%Customer%' THEN NVL(PO_ALLOC,0) END),0) PO_ALLOC_CUST, NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE '%Customer%' THEN NVL(FIRM_WIP_ALLOC,0) END),0) FIRM_WIP_ALLOC_CUST, NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE '%Event%' THEN NVL(OH_ALLOC,0) END),0) OH_ALLOC_EVENT, NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE '%Event%' THEN NVL(IT_ALLOC,0) END),0) IT_ALLOC_EVENT, NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE '%Event%' THEN NVL(PO_ALLOC,0) END),0) PO_ALLOC_EVENT, NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE '%Event%' THEN NVL(FIRM_WIP_ALLOC,0) END),0) FIRM_WIP_ALLOC_EVENT, NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE '%Maxbuild%' THEN NVL(OH_ALLOC,0) END),0) OH_ALLOC_MAXB, NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE '%Maxbuild%' THEN NVL(IT_ALLOC,0) END),0) IT_ALLOC_MAXB, NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE '%Maxbuild%' THEN NVL(PO_ALLOC,0) END),0) PO_ALLOC_MAXB, NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE '%Maxbuild%' THEN NVL(FIRM_WIP_ALLOC,0) END),0) FIRM_WIP_ALLOC_MAXB , NVL(SUM(DISTINCT NVL(orig_onhand_qty,b.onhand_units)),0) onhand_qty , NVL(SUM(DISTINCT NVL(orig_intransit_qty,b.intransit_units)),0) intransit_qty , NVL(SUM(DISTINCT NVL(orig_po_qty,b.po_units)),0) po_qty , NVL(SUM(DISTINCT NVL(orig_firm_wip_qty,b.firm_wip_units)),0) firm_wip_qty , NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_class in $$PARM_DEMAND_CLASS_LIST THEN (CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE 'Customer%' AND spread_critical_ratio <= $$PARM_NEAR_TERM_RATIO THEN NVL(demand_qty,0) ELSE 0 END) ELSE (CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE 'Customer%' AND rule_no <=175 THEN NVL(demand_qty,0) ELSE 0 END) END ),0) week_open_orders_4, NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_class in $$PARM_DEMAND_CLASS_LIST THEN (CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE 'Event%' AND spread_critical_ratio <= $$PARM_NEAR_TERM_RATIO THEN NVL(demand_qty,0) ELSE 0 END) ELSE (CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE 'Event%' AND rule_no <=175 THEN NVL(demand_qty,0) NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE '%Customer%' AND sequence_no = NVL(mx.Max_Seq_Cust,0) THEN NVL(BALANCE_ONHAND_QTY,0) + NVL(BALANCE_INTRANSIT_QTY,0) END),0) OO_EXCESS_OF_FG,
NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE '%Customer%' AND sequence_no = NVL(mx.Max_Seq_Cust,0) THEN NVL(BALANCE_ONHAND_QTY,0) + NVL(BALANCE_INTRANSIT_QTY,0) + NVL(BALANCE_PO_QTY,0) + NVL(BALANCE_FIRM_WIP_QTY,0) END),0) OO_EXCESS_OF_INV, NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE '%TIL%' AND sequence_no = NVL(mx.Max_Seq_Til,0) THEN NVL(BALANCE_ONHAND_QTY,0) END),0) TIL_EXCESS_OF_OH,
NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE '%TIL%' AND sequence_no = NVL(mx.Max_Seq_Til,0) THEN NVL(BALANCE_ONHAND_QTY,0) + NVL(BALANCE_INTRANSIT_QTY,0) END),0) TIL_EXCESS_OF_FG,
NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE '%TIL%' AND sequence_no = NVL(mx.Max_Seq_Til,0) THEN NVL(BALANCE_ONHAND_QTY,0) + NVL(BALANCE_INTRANSIT_QTY,0) + NVL (BALANCE_PO_QTY,0) + NVL(BALANCE_FIRM_WIP_QTY,0) END),0) TIL_EXCESS_OF_INV, NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE '%Event%' AND sequence_no = NVL(mx.Max_Seq_Event,0) THEN NVL(BALANCE_ONHAND_QTY,0) END),0) EVENT_EXCESS_OF_OH,
NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE '%Event%' AND sequence_no = NVL(mx.Max_Seq_Event,0) THEN NVL(BALANCE_ONHAND_QTY,0) + NVL(BALANCE_INTRANSIT_QTY,0) END),0) EVENT_EXCESS_OF_FG,
NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE '%Event%' AND sequence_no = NVL(mx.Max_Seq_Event,0) THEN NVL(BALANCE_ONHAND_QTY,0) + NVL(BALANCE_INTRANSIT_QTY,0) + NVL(BALANCE_PO_QTY,0) + NVL(BALANCE_FIRM_WIP_QTY,0) END),0) EVENT_EXCESS_OF_INV, NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE '%Maxbuild%' AND sequence_no = NVL(mx.Max_Seq_MB,0) THEN NVL(BALANCE_ONHAND_QTY,0) + NVL(BALANCE_INTRANSIT_QTY,0) + NVL(BALANCE_PO_QTY,0) + NVL(BALANCE_FIRM_WIP_QTY,0) END),0) MB_EXCESS_OF_INV,
NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE '%TIL%' AND sequence_no < NVL(mx.Max_Seq_Cust,0) THEN NVL(OH_ALLOC,0) END),0) OH_ALLOC_DCTIL,
NVL(SUM( CASE WHEN demand_source LIKE '%TIL%' AND sequence_no = NVL(mx.Max_Seq_Til,0) AND sequence_no < NVL(mx.Max_Seq_Cust,0) THEN NVL (BALANCE_ONHAND_QTY,0) END),0) DCTIL_EXCESS_OF_OH FROM taser_netting a full outer join (SELECT ITEM_ID, AS_OF_dATE, STYLE_CD, COLOR_CD, SIZE_CD, ATTRIBUTE_CD, DEMAND_LOC, SUM(ONHAND_UNITS) ONHAND_UNITS, SUM(intransit_units) intransit_units, SUM(firm_wip_units) firm_wip_units, SUM(po_units) po_units FROM SUPPLY GROUP BY ITEM_ID, AS_OF_dATE, STYLE_CD, COLOR_CD, SIZE_CD, ATTRIBUTE_CD, DEMAND_LOC ) b on a.item_id=b.item_id and a.dc_code=b.demand_loc and a.as_of_Date= b.as_of_date left outer join dpr_item a2 on a.item_code = a2.item_code and a2.status = 'A' Left outer join (select * from dpr_item where status = 'A' and NOT (manufacturing_product_family= 'DCTIL' and primary_dc = dc_code)) di on b.STYLE_CD =di.aps_style_cd and b.COLOR_CD =di.aps_color_cd and b.SIZE_CD =di.size_code and b.ATTRIBUTE_CD =di.attribute_code and b.DEMAND_LOC =di.dc_code left outer join (select item_id, dc_code, item_code, max(case when demand_source LIKE '%Customer%' then Sequence_No else 0 end) Max_Seq_Cust, max(case when demand_source LIKE '%TIL%' then Sequence_No else 0 end) Max_Seq_Til, max(case when demand_source LIKE '%Event%' then Sequence_No else 0 end) Max_Seq_Event, max(case when demand_source LIKE '%Maxbuild%' then Sequence_No else 0 end) Max_Seq_MB from taser_netting group by item_id, dc_code, item_code) mx ON a.item_id = mx.item_id and a.dc_code = mx.dc_code and a.item_code = mx.item_code GROUP BY nvl(a.as_of_date, b.as_of_date), nvl(a.item_id, b.item_id), nvl(a.item_code, di.item_code), nvl(a.dc_code, b.demand_loc), nvl(a2.aps_style_Cd , b.style_cd), nvl(a2.aps_color_cd, b.color_cd), nvl(a2.size_code, b.size_cd) , nvl(a2.attribute_code, b.attribute_cd)
